data.description: Hazelwood West Schools!  Come check out this great very charming Ranch Style house with 3 bedrooms and 2 baths and a full partially finished basement for you to enjoy. Good size level yard for family and kids to play and entertain. Basement is spacious and just needs some carpeting. Blue Esmeralda Granite tile floor in master bath, 6 panel doors, some thermal windows, and hardwood floors throughout.  Don't wait any longer and schedule viewing today.
